Nissan.title: Nissan
Nissan.description: [Itermediate] Start vehicles near you. Extend your arms and perform (inverse) ignition

freeze.title: freeze
freeze.description: [Beginner] Freeze your opponent for 10 secs. Hold your wand looking up. Don't move it

lumen.title: Lumen
lumen.description: [Beginner]. Turn the lights up and down. Hold your wand looking up. Move your arm from left to right in a straight line

comics.title: comics
comics.description: [Intermediate] Make fun of things. Reverse the magic to your opponent. Hold your wand bent approx 70 degrees. Make a line with your arm, from the bottom left to the top right corner.

invitation.title: Invitation
invitation.description: [Intermediate] Pull objects new you. You need to start with your arms bent (in fron of your body), then straighten them.

Circus.title: Circus
Circus.description: [Difficult] Causes serious damage to your opponents blood circulation. Make a circle in the air in front of you (clockwise direction). Start from the bottom.

die.title: Die
die.description: [Intermediate] Punish your opponent. Hold your wand in front of you and poke once. Like with a bayonette

boxing.title: Boxing
boxing.description: [Hard] Box three times to in front of you.

photo.title: Photo
photo.description: [Easy] Paralize your opponent for 3 secods. Hold your wand facing the opponent.
